                    דרחמנה ומן עמלה<lb/> אמן אמן סלה</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b2">
                <p>[Remember for good so-and-so] who donated this lintel from the Merciful [One] and
                    from his [own] property. Amen, Amen, Selah.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>"The piece is unusual in that it shows two aediculae flanking a menorah, and not
                    menorahs on either side of a Torah Shrine."</p>
            </div>
